This directory contains the basic MCT source code.

MCT distribution contents:
MCT/
MCT/COPYRIGHT
MCT/doc/
MCT/examples/
MCT/mct/   <- You are here
MCT/mpeu/
MCT/protex/

A complete distribution of MCT can be obtained from http://www.mcs.anl.gov/mct.

---------------------------------------------------
Build instructions:
In the top level, type "make" to build mct and mpeu.

If ./configure was already run and mpeu was already built,
you can type "make" in this directory.

---------------------------------------------------
